    bibo:startPage "59" ;
    bibo:volume "1675" ;
    dc:creator "Duellman, William E.; Hedges, Blair" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "Two new minute species of Phrynopus (Lissamphibia: Anura) from the Cordillera oriental in Peru" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274058> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.274058>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Species of Phrynopus: (A) P. auriculatus, KU 261633, male holotype, 13.4 mm SVL; (B) P. tribulosus, KU 261630, male holotype, 15.2 mm SVL.; (C) P. peruanus, MTD 46802, male, 22.5 mm SVL, from Puna of Maraynioc, Pasco, Peru; (D) P. dagmarae, MHNSM 20453, male, 26.6 mm SVL, from 15 km SE Maraypata, Huánuco, Peru. A and B by S. B. Hedges; C and D by E. Lehr." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/274058/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

